As a property renter, I want to search properties based on criterias like the price, number of rooms and the year the house was built.


As a property renter, I want to request a visit to see the house.


As a property renter, I want to filter the houses according to their price, number of rooms, living lot area dimensions, time in the market, building type, year built.


As a property renter, I want to search for brokers and see what houses are under their supervision.


As a property renter, I want to have a monthly payment calculator to estimate the financial needs.


As a property renter, I want to save favorites houses for easy access.


As a property renter, I want to see images of the houses to have a better idea if the house is worth visiting.


As a property renter, I want to have a profile that displays my personal information, my broker, my appointments, my visit requests and my saved houses.

As a property renter, I want to make an account.

As a property renter, I want to reset my password.

As a property renter, I want to have 2-factor authorization.

As a property renter, I want to see the different types of contracts being offered. 

As a property renter, I want to be able to see what ammenities are included and whats not.
